Oh.

[[div class="declaration red"]]

= [[size 105%]]**STATUS OF INTERRUPTIONS**[[/size]]

------

* YOU ARE THE VICTIM OF AN [[span class="element"]]ADVANCING CRIMINAL ELEMENT[[/span]].
 * THIS [[span class="element"]]INTRUDER[[/span]] HAS GUTTED A CENTURIES-OLD ESSOPLEX, THEREBY KILLING REALITY AND ITS PERMUTATIONS.
  * YOU HAVE THE POWER TO ANNIHILATE THIS [[span class="element"]]OBSTRUCTION[[/span]].

[[/div]]

You feel an urge to kill and maim and maul rising in your muscles, and your Absentia Cocoon seethes.

[[div class="declaration red"]]

* FOR TWO HUNDRED YEARS WE CONTROLLED THIS ROCK.
