* AND YOU ARE ITS CHILD.
* WE ASK ONLY ONE THING.
 * ONLY ONE MIRACLE, FROM THE LAST INCARNATUM OF GODHOOD.

* WE ASK YOU KILL THE [[span class="element"]]SERPENT[[/span]].

