[[div class="declaration green element"]]
**SCP-001** - //Advancing Criminal Element//

------

[[include :scp-wiki:component:coltop show=ASSESS | hide=RETREAT]]
[[<]]
[[div class="terminal t-real"]]

[[div class="scptop-wrap"]]
[[div class="scptop-bg"]]
[[=image breaker.png]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="scptop-content desktop-display"]]
SCP-001 @@ @@ — @@ @@ Keter
[[/div]]
[[div class="scptop-content mobile-display"]]
SCP-001
